                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170115-187-off1020 t18170115-187-cd1021"></join>, one bed, value 3l.; one bolster, value 1s.; one sheet, value 1s.; one quilt, value 2s.; and three blankets, value 10s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18170115-187-victim1350" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Mecham
