                     </persName>
                     
                  , the same goods being in a lodging-room, in the dwelling house of the said, 
                     <persName id="t18170115-187-person1351">
                        Thomas 
                        Mecham
                     <interp inst="t18170115-187-person1351" type="surname" value="Mecham"></interp>
